events.title: Food Truck Fest at Westlake Park
events.description: Spice up your lunch break with the return of Food Truck Fest! On the third Wednesday of each month, five local trucks will take over the park with a mini food court of options. Stop by from 11 a.m.-2 p.m. for lunch and live music. The Fest will return each month on the third Wednesday through August.

events.title: Earth Day Market at Westlake Park
events.description: Shop with a purpose while supporting the small business community at the Earth Day Market at Westlake Park! Browse more than 20 local artisans and makers for handcrafted goods, upcycled treasures and earth-friendly products and gifts. We’ll also have live music and a free DIY activity hosted by local artist Moses Sun, where you can create your own upcycled art. We’ll see you there!
